      Abstract:
        'Testing is an important aspect in object oriented programming. Testing is done in three levels namely Unit, Integration and System. Testing is also classified into three main strategies, they are Structural, black-box, error-driven strategies. In this project, we propose an object-oriented testing technique “Mutation” and object oriented metrics are implemented using Selenium tool and a data mining application that will test the object oriented code to reduce the time complexity and increase the performance of the software. Mutation way of examining is utilized to create new software test cases and to examine the quality of already existing programs. Selenium tool is an open source technology it will automate web applications for testing purpose. It provides a set of various software equipments each with a different way to support testing that is generated automatically. The proposed System Implement the selenium tool into the mutation testing to test the object oriented coding. © Research India Publications.',
